<i>♪ Shinin' brighter</i>
<i>than a thousand suns ♪</i>

02:17.990 --> 02:19.750
<i>♪ Is this really love? </i>

02:19.950 --> 02:21.670
<i>♪ There's no need to rush </i>

02:21.870 --> 02:23.360
<i>♪ Life has just begun </i>

02:23.560 --> 02:26.110
<i>both: ♪ Life has just begun </i>

02:26.310 --> 02:28.280
<i>- ♪ You're brave</i>
<i>as you are brilliant ♪</i>

02:28.480 --> 02:33.420
<i>♪ Your radiance</i>
<i>is like a million lights ♪</i>

02:33.620 --> 02:37.160
<i>♪ A goddess on high,</i>
<i>a colorful mind ♪</i>

02:37.360 --> 02:39.120
<i>♪ You mesmerize </i>

02:39.320 --> 02:40.690
<i>both: ♪ You mesmerize </i>

02:40.890 --> 02:42.640
- [clears throat]
<i>- ♪ And he's just </i>

02:42.840 --> 02:44.560
<i>♪ He's just </i>

