<i>♪ He's not worth your time </i>

03:02.560 --> 03:05.060
<i>♪ So lose that guy </i>

03:05.260 --> 03:07.060
<i>- ♪ You can do</i>
<i>a whole lot better ♪</i>

03:07.260 --> 03:10.240
<i>♪ Than this khaki-wearing</i>
<i>old man creeper ♪</i>

03:10.440 --> 03:12.370
<i>both: ♪ Old man creeper </i>

03:12.570 --> 03:13.890
<i>♪ Don't settle for less </i>

03:14.090 --> 03:15.590
<i>♪ You deserve the best </i>

03:15.790 --> 03:18.250
<i>♪ You're a double feature </i>

03:18.450 --> 03:19.330
<i>both: ♪ A double feature </i>

03:19.530 --> 03:21.340
<i>♪ And he's just </i>

03:21.540 --> 03:23.340
<i>♪ He's just </i>

03:23.540 --> 03:26.380
<i>♪ He's just </i>

03:26.580 --> 03:28.170
<i>A geriatric teacher.</i>

03:28.370 --> 03:30.780
<i>- And his name is Leonard,</i>
<i>for God's sake!</i>

03:30.980 --> 03:32.480
<i>all:</i>
<i>♪ Please, please, please </i>

03:32.680 --> 03:34.740
<i> ♪ Please, please don't do it </i>

03:34.940 --> 03:38.310
<i>♪ You're bee's knees,</i>
<i>stop being foolish ♪</i>

03:38.510 --> 03:42.180
<i>♪ You're pie in the sky,</i>
<i>the apple of eyes ♪</i>

